> In zsh, you can do something like:
> 
> ${(l:20::?:)~:-} for .{20}
> 
> and
> 
> ${(l:20::?:)~:-}${(l:40::(?|))~:-}
> 
> for .{20,30}
> 
> but that's a bit convoluted.
> 
> See also ${${(r:30:):-${(l:20::.:):-}}:gs: :(?|)::gs/./?}
> 

